translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ビヨンホウはコップの端を合わせた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Biyonghou clinked his glass against the rim.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「がははははははははは！！！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gahahahahahahaha!!!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うひひひひひひひひひ！！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Uhihihihihihihi!!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「呑め！　おら、呑めえ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Drink! Come on, drink!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「呑んでますよう！　うひょひょひょひょ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm drinking, you know! Uhyo hyohyo hyohyo!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぐびぐびぐび！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: *gulp gulp gulp!*"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 二人は嗜むという領域をあっさり越えていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The two of them had easily surpassed the realm of mere tasting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぐわぁっはっはっはっは！！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Guahaha hahahaha!!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なかなかいい酒だな！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This is quite some good sake!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺様にはジュース程度だが！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Though to me, it's just like juice!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うへへへへ！　流石は総統閣下ですなあ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Uhehehe! As expected of the Supreme Commander!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ささ！　まだまだいきましょう！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Come on! Let's keep going!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うおー！　俺様は人間水力発電所だー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Whoa! I'm like a human hydroelectric power plant!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぐびぐびぐび！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: *gulp gulp gulp!*"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ビヨンホウに注がせるまま、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Letting Biyonghou pour it,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは喉に酒を流し込んでいく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance poured the sake down his throat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あああああああうああああああ！！！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Aaaaaaah uaaaaah!!!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なっちゃいないんだ〜〜〜〜〜〜！！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's not getting me drunk~~~~!!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ごふぅ、と酒臭い息が漏れ出る。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A wine-breath was let out with a coughing sound.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「娘がねえ、娘が！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "My daughter, you know, my daughter!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もうお父さんとお風呂入りたくないって
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She says she doesn't want to take a bath with her dad anymore.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言うんですよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's what she says!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あー、お前の娘か？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, your daughter?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 咥えるのがけっこう上手くてグッドだぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She's pretty good at taking it in her mouth, pretty good."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうその娘！　うあああああーー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yeah, that daughter! Uaaaaaah---!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これまではまだ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Until now,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 土下座すればどうにかなってたのに！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I could somehow manage if I grovelled on my knees!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「土下座なんぞしとったのかお前……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You were grovelling on your knees or something...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「父親なんてねえ、損なもんですよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Being a father is such a losing role.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんなに可愛い生き物はいないと、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I've always believed there's no creature as cute as my daughter,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ずっと娘に愛情注いできたのに！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and have poured all my love into her!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「がはははは。娘なんて鬱陶しいだけだろ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gahahahaha. Daughters are just annoying, don't you think?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自分のじゃ手も出せないんだぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You can't even lay a hand on your own kid."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でも可愛いでしょう！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But isn't she cute!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「可愛いからむかつくんだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "She's cute, so that just pisses me off!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「甘やかしたくなるでしょう！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Makes you want to spoil her, right!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「む……甘やかして……なーい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Mmm... Spoil her... I'm not doing that!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 厳格な父親だぞー、俺様はー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm a strict father, I am!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あはははははは！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ahahahahaha!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これ、めっちゃ甘やかしてるパターンだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This is totally the 'spoiling her' pattern!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でもねでもね！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But you know! But you know!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつかは嫁に行くんですよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Someday, she'll get married!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんだとぅ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What did you say?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お父さん、今までありがとう……なんて！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "'Thank you, Dad, for everything until now'... something like that!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言われて！　もう号泣！　とか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She'd say that and then break down crying! Or something!"
"Ba"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ばば」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Baba"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「む……甘やかして……なーい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Mmm... Spoil her... I'm not doing that!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 厳格な父親だぞー、俺様はー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm a strict father, I am!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あはははははは！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ahahahahaha!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これ、めっちゃ甘やかしてるパターンだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This is totally the 'spoiling her' pattern!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でもねでもね！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But you know! But you know!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつかは嫁に行くんですよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Someday, she'll get married!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんだとぅ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What did you say?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お父さん、今までありがとう……なんて！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "'Thank you, Dad, for everything until now'... something like that!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言われて！　もう号泣！　とか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She'd say that and then break down crying! Or something!"
"Ba"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ばば」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Baba"
